    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 8. Selitrichodes neseri female: 3, dosolateral habitus; 4, head in frontal view; 5, antenna in lateral view; 6, mesosoma in dorsal view; 7, wing in dorsal view; 8, metasoma in dorsal view." ;
