    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213856>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 11. 9 and 10, Selitrichodes neseri male: 9, dosolateral habitus; 10, antenna in lateral view. 11, Selitrichodes neseri eggs on a pupa of Leptocybe invasa (more than one egg probably a cage artefact) (Photo: Stefan Neser)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213856/files/figure.png" ;
